{
  "text": "The current experimental limit on the anomalous magnetic moment of the tau lepton is rather weak, but it can be improved in the future [CITATION_1] :",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "119207374"
  },
  "bib_entries": {
    "119207374": {
      "title": "Towards a determination of the tau lepton dipole moments",
      "abstract": "The \u03c4 anomalous magnetic moment a\u03c4 and electric dipole moment d\u03c4 have not yet been observed. The present bounds on their values are of order 10\u22122 and 10\u221217e cm, respectively. We propose to measure a\u03c4 with a precision of O(10\u22123) or better and improve the existing limits on d\u03c4 using precise \u03c4\u2212\u2192l\u2212\u03bd\u03c4\u03bd\u00afl\u03b3 (l=e or \u03bc) data from high-luminosity B factories. A detailed feasibility study of this method is underway."
    }
  }
}